com.axelor.studio.service.wkf

Class WkfTrackingService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.axelor.studio.service.wkf.WkfTrackingService

  • public class WkfTrackingService
extends java.lang.Object
    Service handle tracking of workflow instance for particular record. Creates WkfTracking, WkfTrackingLine, WkfTrackingTime and WkfTrackingTotal records.
    Author:
    axelor

      • track

        public void track(java.lang.String model,
         java.lang.Long modelId,
         java.lang.String status)
        Root method to access the service. It create WkfTracking record. WkfTracking is linked with record of model and workflow of model.
        Parameters:
        model - Model having workflow.
        modelId - Record id of model to track.
        status - Current wkfStatus of record.

      • updateTrackingLine

        public WkfTrackingLine updateTrackingLine(WkfTracking wkfTracking,
                                 java.lang.String status)
        Method add new WkfTrackingLine in WkfTracking for given status if that status is not last status added.
        Parameters:
        wkfTracking - WkfTracking to update with new line.
        status - Status to check for update.
        Returns:
        WkfTrackingLine created or return null if status not changed.

      • updateTrackingTotal

        public void updateTrackingTotal(WkfTracking wkfTracking,
                       java.lang.String status)
        Update o2m to WkfTrackingTotal in WkfTracking. Create or Update WkfTrackingTotal for given status with updated count of status.
        Parameters:
        wkfTracking - WkfTracking to update for WkfTrackingTotal.
        status - Status to check for total update.

      • updateTrackingTime

        public void updateTrackingTime(WkfTracking wkfTracking,
                      java.lang.String status)
        This method create or update WkfTrackingTime record for given WkfTracking and status. For existing WkfTrackingTime it update total time in days and hours.
        Parameters:
        wkfTracking - WkfTracking to update for WkfTrackingTime.
        status - Status to check for WkfTrackingTime.
